com.myappcompany.user.safeparkingzones

Class ParkingSpotStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.myappcompany.user.safeparkingzones.ParkingSpotStats

  • public class ParkingSpotStats
extends java.lang.Object
    Finds the given statistics for each parking spot currently displayed on the screen. It represents each of the parking spots as a vertex and those that are within 0.2 km are considered adjacent. The graph is meant to show the relationships between the vertices and their information as well, creating a web of inter-connected parkingSpots
    Author:
    Orlando Ortega
